Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<EYECATCH>

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:05.60,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, obtained two powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.23,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.28,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to give an order to anyone. A power that enforces absolute obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:13.65,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The other is the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:18.89,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,His personal army formed to destroy the Britannia Empire, ruled by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.45,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch has started to act by using the code name "Zero"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:30.71,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,in order to avenge his mother and turn the world into a place that his sister, Nanali, can live happily in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.68,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of results will those actions bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.87,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,570)}Right now, no one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? A Britannian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit too daring for a spy? Is he an ideologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.51,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this good? The number of hopeful applicants has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though I hate Britannia, I don't support activities like terrorism."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.32,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the majority of the Elevens feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:55.28,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a large population of the Elevens supports the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:58.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, it's easier for the Order to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not having the people leaking our movements out to the government is already a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:08.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The group in Kyoto said that they'll provide us with Knightmares, and the information offered to us has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese can't resist the lure of a stampede. {Best attempt I can to fit stampede in there... basically, he's implying that Japanese has a pack mentality.}{Domino effect? Peer pressure? I don't know...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:15.00,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we create a reason that they can identify with...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.05,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,So you created the "allies of justice" thing for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone loves them, don't they? The allies of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.55,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the face of an ally of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:30.67,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I've been demoted, like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.43,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.11,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't intend for things to just end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.24,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,You feel the same way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.09,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.01,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,We've found some clues about Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:46.82,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,The private establishment, Ashford Academy. I wish for you to investigate the male students there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.67,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I think one of Zero's supporters is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:53.39,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Due to military duties, we have no choice but to head towards the Narita mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.17,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,During that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.34,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Narita?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.90,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,According to the rumors, that's where the main base of the Japanese Liberation Front is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.66,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.80,Default,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.71,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.80,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is a Glasgow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.89,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,They're called Burai. They were remodeled in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.99,Default,Knight02,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.82,Default,Knight03,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights sure is powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.79,Default,Knight04,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't easy to get in though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.19,Default,Knight05,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we're the elite of the elite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.27,Default,Knight06,0000,0000,0000,,I'm burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:26.28,Default,Knight07,0000,0000,0000,,Those people in Kyoto sent this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.70,Default,Knight08,0000,0000,0000,,This is a true blue, completely made in Japan Knightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.01,Default,Knight09,0000,0000,0000,,Guren Mk. II...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.23,Default,Knight10,0000,0000,0000,,What does the user manual say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.54,Default,Knight09,0000,0000,0000,,The "Radiation Wave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.54,Default,Knight11,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amazing weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.57,Default,Knight02,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.21,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,This means the famous people in Kyoto have recognized us, the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:41.83,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.47,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,How should we use this equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.57,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll come over there. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.26,Default,Knight09,0000,0000,0000,,The newcomers sure are helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not only Tamaki, but Inoue and the others are also excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:59.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Kyoto has provided assistance to other resistances as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.86,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We've finally become one of those they support...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No. You are mistaken, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.13,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.62,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Just getting this much attention from them is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:15.86,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,This...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Guren Mk. II is yours, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.81,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Mine? But, right now, the number of members we have is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.27,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Also, given the defensive capabilities of the Guren, you should be the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are the ace pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.56,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I am just the commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I will just use the Burai since you are the trump card in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you have a reason to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:35.75,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.52,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:42.65,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,A strange piece of information has arrived from the Britannian who wants to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.73,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be a trap to lure us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.35,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out more, but it's dangerous to approach this man recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.00,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,But this information is too important to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.03,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.50,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go hiking this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.37,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.71,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Up the Narita mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.21,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:07.62,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Sayoko-san, there's no need to prepare Brother's breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.83,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he's going on a vacation for three days, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.25,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.56,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, he's been going out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.86,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it with a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.52,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.63,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Region five, no abnormalities sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.86,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. The next scheduled communication will take place in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:31.16,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Like anything abnormal would happen out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:35.10,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Japanese Liberation Front, have influence over this area. It won't be easy to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.49,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.79,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. I just came here to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for you to ignore them... all of the abnormalities...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.88,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.47,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.62,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush me. You're an expert at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.72,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed Zero's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.27,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,We'll move to point two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.56,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't Zero use the wireless communicator in his Burai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.45,Default,Knight02,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what does he mean by "hiking"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.30,Default,Knight03,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe military training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.58,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Zero is somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.32,Default,Knight04,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me we're going to dig up a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.37,Default,Knight05,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why we brought an excavator along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.12,Default,Knight05,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.96,Default,Knight05,0000,0000,0000,,Karen, did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:25.67,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:26.94,Default,Knight05,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Ougi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.17,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:32.09,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is avoiding having his transmission traced...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.97,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.82,Default,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia, the day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:44.35,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's been confirmed that the main base of the Japanese Liberation Front is within this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.94,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We have divided our four main units into seven, and they are waiting in ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:53.45,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-general, they are awaiting your command. Once it's issued, we will surround and destroy them in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.93,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a chance that enemies will appear from outside of our enclosure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.71,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.16,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:04.56,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Right as the operation commences, we will close the neighboring roads and the mountain roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.50,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We have back-up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:09.46,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It would be Zero's last appearance if he were to act recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.55,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.75,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,You say you want to meet her, but do you even realize who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.54,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,She's a princess, and we're mere commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.28,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,You call it fate as a result of the hoteljacking, but what kind of fate is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:22.11,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But... I haven't said thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.81,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,to Princess Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:27.98,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Well, we could've done that before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:32.24,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how high of a social status do you think the granddaughter of a principal has?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.96,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... so-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.49,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... so-so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,C.C., what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.53,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that I would protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Pretending to be a guardian...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.55,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, why are you Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to discuss philosophy with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:54.58,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,You changed your family name to Lamperouge, but you left your first name as Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:56.85,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,How naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:58.53,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to give up the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, your "C.C." is weird too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.72,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even a human name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.59,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.48,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why the snow is white?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:17.21,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Because it forgot what color it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.99,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,All troops are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.36,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.90,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,As planned, Euphemia will stay at G1 and support us from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.92,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Give command of the medical troops to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.18,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.03,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:32.06,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Guilford? Is it about Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:35.07,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shouldn't we have made her stay at the government office?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.43,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,She was unexpectedly stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.58,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she wanted to see a real battle with her own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.10,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.07,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,What's that unit in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.35,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's the back-up troop with an Eleven pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.43,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that Lancelot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:53.94,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, having a Number pilot a Knightmare wasn't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.23,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,However, that unit is one that was authorized by His Highness, the second prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.66,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Even with our military powers, we are unable to interfere with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.29,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,They hope that we provide them with as much actual combat to participate in as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.22,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we really going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.75,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's an army that has considerable strength within Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.20,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should cooperate with the Japanese Liberation Front...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even as things are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ougi, you don't believe in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.33,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.30,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who wanted and asked you to be our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.60,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's only one answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.10,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.50,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-general, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.44,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Commence the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.57,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese Liberation Front...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.29,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Are they a group that has fallen behind the times?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.78,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Or are they a group that has forgotten self-respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.91,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time for you and your magical dream to become one and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.83,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.28,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian army has surrounded the entire Narita mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.92,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We have identified more than 100 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.83,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.08,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.55,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be completely surrounded by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.66,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be an escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We're already sealed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.18,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to live, we have no choice but to fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.47,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? Against Britannia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.22,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to go head-on with them?! We're already surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.26,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but our enemy is Cornelia's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.44,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful enemy that's different from what we've been fighting against!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:21.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a miracle if we emerge victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.73,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, at a time like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:29.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A messiah will not be recognized until he makes a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, we will need a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.92,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miracles don't happen so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.44,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're damn useless as a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.26,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All paths of retreat have been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:51.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you think that you can win without me, feel free to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You've had only two choices ever since you joined the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:10.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Either live with me, or die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.75,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.36,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Our nearby supporters have all been captured too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:23.13,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,General Katase, there's a transmission from Cornelia's army asking us to surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:27.81,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, if we give up now, the Japanese liberation movement will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.52,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Then General, are we taking an aggressive approach, or a defensive one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.98,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou... What is Toudou doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.10,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,He went to Kyoto to pick up the Burai Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.69,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Shisaiken is traveling with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.87,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,According to schedule, they should be back soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.49,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.16,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Burai, prepare to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.66,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the corners of the enclosure and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.36,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,The pride and honor of Japan is at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.84,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to make our comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:59.87,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's main base should be inside the mountain, but we are unable to pinpoint the exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:04.76,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,However, in order to obtain the list of their supporters, we cannot perform an aerial assault on their main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:10.14,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy would aim for one of the corners of our enclosure and try to break out from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.09,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Once they do that, we will be able to identify the location of their main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.27,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Three of our units will be going head-on with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:19.52,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,They are the units lead by General Darlton, General Alex, and Governor-general Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.09,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,As for our flank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.11,Note,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Note: ECM stands for Electronic Countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.11,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It's the enemy's ECM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.13,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is going to appear soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.22,Note,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Note: ECCM stands for Electronic Counter-Countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.09,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,We should activate our ECCM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.91,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Switch the communication channel over to Alpha 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.27,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's... what is it called again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.56,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The Burai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.49,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Just be careful of the thing that looks like a Glasgow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:38.58,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.09,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,So, this mountain has been transformed into a fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.76,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, please stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.39,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Guilford, don't treat me like those other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.36,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:53.72,Default,Burai00,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.60,Default,Burai00,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.81,Default,Burai01,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! Take the head of their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.64,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.10,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.03,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,We shall cover you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.33,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I, Cornelia, am here now! Isn't there anyone who wants to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:16.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try and challenge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.50,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.04,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.17,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,An order has been given to evacuate this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:32.27,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anyone left, please take refuge quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.95,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, an order has been given to evacuate this region...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.91,Default,Scientist00,0000,0000,0000,,Why was this place chosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.58,Default,Scientist00,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will become meaningless if the army discovers Code R's test data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:45.25,Default,Scientist01,0000,0000,0000,,We initially thought that, since we're inside the terrorists' area of influence, it would be harder for them to track us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.82,Default,Scientist02,0000,0000,0000,,General Padre was the one who decided that. Even if you bring it up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.37,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.35,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's fire has started to intensify over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.66,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,This might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:58.71,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Spread apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.74,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless. We've lost communication with our second wave of attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.41,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,What overwhelming power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.40,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,General Darlton, by analyzing the objective of the enemy's movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:15.63,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,we've determined that the entrance to the main base of the Japanese Liberation Front should be that mountain cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.02,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Should I say "bingo" in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.59,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's more along the lines of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.81,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Go along with me, honest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.90,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... Darlton?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.55,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's main base is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.82,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we shall wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.99,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.10,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to take credit for my subordinates' work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.48,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Send the reserve troops to Darlton's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.12,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get yet another medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A well thought-out tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But the more elaborate your tactic is, the easier it is to see past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This includes your location as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.64,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't the reserve troops supposed to gather where General Darlton is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:57.86,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But our unit is supposed to wait behind Governor-general Cornelia's unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.14,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,You call this behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.85,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,This is the outskirt of the outskirt of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.34,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,How am I going to regain my honor at a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.95,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Communication with Nakamura squadron, terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.75,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,No reaction from region three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:10.92,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Major Tabata was killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.40,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroda and Kumada have been killed too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.76,Default,???05,0000,0000,0000,,What is Nagoya doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.34,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.69,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,If Toudou were here, the divine wind would blow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.29,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the miracle of Itsukushima once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.46,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we being a bit overbearing, Toudou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.46,Default,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina, Chiba, prepare the Burai Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.71,Default,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to Urabe and Senba in the car behind us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.98,Default,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,All the roads leading into Narita are being restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.94,Default,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Things have started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.63,Default,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hope we make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.11,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the power of the anti-government forces in Area 11 will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.61,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:50.91,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.56,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Our preparations are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All members of the Order of the Black Knights, prepare to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.33,Default,Knight00,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, guess we have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.39,Default,Knight01,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.91,Default,Knight02,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to make a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.29,Default,Knight03,0000,0000,0000,,We have Zero with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:07.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on, we, the Order of the Black Knights, shall head down the mountain and ambush the Britannian army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once I give my orders, dash straight to point three with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The aim of our operation is to capture the second princess of Britannia, Cornelia, alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.14,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will clear the path for us is the Guren Mk. II.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Karen, make use of piercing electrode number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do it with one decisive blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:26.06,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.82,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Checking the power output. Radiation Wave activated. Atmosphere under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.24,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,External discharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.21,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.38,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.30,Default,Burai00,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, is it an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.40,Default,Burai01,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.00,Default,Glasgow,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.11,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.15,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Such a huge landslide...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.29,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, Alex's and Darlton's units will be completely eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.28,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Climb up! Head towards higher ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.50,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.88,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We're still evaluating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.74,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency, please step back. It's dangerous over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.96,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! Where's Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.45,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and figure out Darlton's situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.37,Default,Katase,0000,0000,0000,,Can this place hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.22,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is the epicenter, it should somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.30,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my. They will be washed off to the bottom of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.35,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,There was a heat reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.21,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that someone purposely caused a steam explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.12,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.49,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible unless they use an Electrical Wave or a Radiation Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.80,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:55.27,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it has nothing to do with us. You just continue to stand by in your machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was more destructive than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:10.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we have already managed to split up Cornelia's personal unit, we need to divide it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:15.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The physics teacher... no, it was Nina who helped me with the calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.94,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We have confirmed another unit that is stationed on top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.05,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Kalius's unit has gone to intercept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.83,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to make use of the confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:25.87,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency transmission from Kalius's unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:26.22,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.43,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the Japanese Liberation Front!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.83,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:31.63,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:32.34,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.59,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.01,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.44,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah, if you leave your position without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:38.99,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.60,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me if you wish to be powerful once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:44.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia's reinforcements have been restrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:45.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Finish them off in one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.12,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:53.80,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, our mission is to protect the backs of Zero and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.71,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:00.00,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Kalius's unit was completely wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.31,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I must end things before Zero meets up with Governor-general Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.38,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.16,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Villetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.59,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,So you have come...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:10.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting with one's back to the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected a tactic from an old classic to be this effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:13.44,Note,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Lelouch is referring to a tactic used in the Chu-Han War.\Nhttp://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chu-Han_War#Recovery_of_Han
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.10,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:16.74,Default,Burai,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.02,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Is Zero here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.64,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,If you're around, fight with me... fight with me, Jeremiah Gottwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're still in the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:33.50,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to deal with you, Orange-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:38.09,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-O-range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.08,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.80,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:48.64,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere, this is {\i1}my{\i0}  duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.31,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,But... this is the first time we've seen a Knightmare like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.64,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the Elevens have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.56,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,How could those putrid Elevens have that kind of technology?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:20:59.94,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.51,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.06,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,This guy eliminated Kalius's unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.91,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it, Britannia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:11.04,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally we can fight at the same level as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.25,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,This Guren Mk. II signifies the start of our counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.42,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.66,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,There's something about that right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:19.95,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I get away from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:21.58,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:27.68,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.57,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.16,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah, eject!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.04,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:47.27,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,How could I do that? Zero is... Zero is right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.08,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Don't activate yet, auto-eject!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:56.09,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I have... I have... Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:09.39,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose as long as I have the Guren Mk. II!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:12.24,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeremiah was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.31,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights... what the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:18.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All of the conditions have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:20.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The pieces are all in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:23.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to checkmate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.87,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.70,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even Cornelia knows that her chances of victory are slim now that her forces are divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:03.67,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have the Guren Mk. II on my side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:07.63,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I must capture her alive so that she can tell me the truth behind Mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:10.55,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, capturing her alive would be a great victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.42,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's nothing irregular happening to the Order of the Black Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
